Program: Omnibus
Title: Air Crash Detectives
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jzq
Last Broadcast Date: 05 December 1990
What causes aeroplane crashes? A look at the job of air accident investigators who visit crash sites around the world to find out why individual incidents have happened so they can be prevented from ever happening again. Includes an interview with pilot Eric Moody.